snippet.title: Johnny Depp Deserves Better!
snippet.description:
We made it! 

2020 is almost officially over and we wanted to discuss some of the craziest moments of an unprecedented year. From Johnny Depp being accused of being a wife beater, Lori Loughlin being locked up (have mercy), and Meghan and Harry leaving the comforts of the Royal Palace, also known as MEGXIT.

We would love to hear your favorite story of 2020 in the comments below. 

As always, if you enjoyed, please like, share, & SUBSCRIBE.

We will see you all in 2021. Stay safe, stay sane, and be kind.

Add us on Instagram:
